        <abstract> 
<p>Does not think sermon by E. B. Pusey [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">11763</hi>] is worth a reply. HNR may quote CD as saying that Pusey is "mistaken in imagining that I wrote the Origin with any relation whatever to Theology". Pusey’s attack will be powerless to retard belief in evolution.</p> 
        </abstract>
